{"tid":2099654,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"李偲嫣胞兄涉拒捕被控 辯稱遭李偲嫣誣告metoo 反駁後屢遭人上門滋擾","createTime":"2020-07-08T11:37:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T12:01:12.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1a31f848ff577faea90f6dc56f2ab6ab1bd16c28","tid":2099654,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T11:37:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200708/LAXLG2HHCT63NOVNHMKCI2OTVU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200708%2FLAXLG2HHCT63NOVNHMKCI2OTVU%2F&d=68p4wiGQQ1h%2Fwz3iobjDKy%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=e3bdb958\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200708%2FLAXLG2HHCT63NOVNHMKCI2OTVU%2F&h=17327b5b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200708/LAXLG2HHCT63NOVNHMKCI2OTVU/</a><br />\n<br />\n正義聯盟創黨主席李偲嫣的胞兄李首穎，被指牽涉40多年前一宗非禮案。警方上門調查時，李首穎及兒子被指拒捕及襲警。案件今於觀塘裁判法院續審，李首穎出庭自辯，指與妻子前年向李偲嫣追債後，李偲嫣隨即對他作出「metoo誣告」；及後李首穎透過傳媒作出澄清反駁，自此一家多次受到滋擾，常常有人按門鈴，開門後卻不見人影。"},{"pid":"e1f293b6f4a23b1fbf4fe532593fbd43f76d2fb5","tid":2099654,"uid":156542,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T11:40:11.000Z","msg":"痴鳩線嘅 <br />\n40幾年前 <br />\n而家先講 <br />\n有乜撚證據呀"},{"pid":"8e8473fe5ef21e1b71c4dc07f30d13ef3271b9fc","tid":2099654,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1f293b6f4a23b1fbf4fe532593fbd43f76d2fb5","tid":2099654,"uid":156542,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T11:40:11.000Z","msg":"痴鳩線嘅 <br />\n40幾年前 <br />\n而家先講 <br />\n有乜撚證據呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T11:52:27.000Z","msg":"呢家人都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"621036c284ea67509098bb6f4a696b4b9f28cd4c","tid":2099654,"uid":241804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":